Scalable content generation and alignment across languages

ğŸ” A Standard with a Future
TLS7 is designed to evolve. As computational tools advance, additional layers or refinements may be introducedâ€”e.g., semantic disambiguation, dynamic glossing, embedded audio, visual aids, and multilingual cross-alignment.

